content: mtbc: Merged a significant PR #3458 that fixed agent character plugin construction for the runtime, involving substantial code changes (+55,735/-26,571 lines) across 421 files. Has an open PR #3267 related to teaching the Zilliqa plugin about PlunderSwap currency exchange. Demonstrated sporadic activity, being active on only 4 out of 28 days, with contributions primarily focused on code (63%), configuration (25%), and documentation (13%).
